<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
    <head>
        <title>Shareables | jafner.com</title>
        <meta charset="utf-8">
        <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
        <link rel="stylesheet" href="style.css">
    </head>

    <body>
        <header>
            <h1><a href="index.html">jafner.com</a></h1>
            <hr>
        </header>

        <main>
            
            <div id="nav-placeholder"></div>

            <section id="gifts" class="content-section">
                <h2>Gift Ideas for Jeff</h2>
                <p>Here are some ideas of things I might want</p>
               
                    <article class="gift-item">
                        <h3 class="gift-title">Classic Give'r Gloves - Size: Large, Waxed: Yes</h3>
                        <p class="gift-description">I really like the heavier Give'r gloves and mittens I have - these would be nice for warmer weather (and I wouldn't say no to having them embossed)</p>
                        <p><a href="https://www.give-r.com/products/classic-giver-gloves" class="gift-link" target="_blank">Give'r's Site</a></p>
                    </article>
                    
                    <article class="gift-item">
                        <h3 class="gift-title">Darn Tough socks - Size: Medium</h3>
                        <p class="gift-description">My current favorite socks - very durable so far and comfortable, any of their styles should do, though prefer not black socks</p>
                        <p><a href="https://darntough.com/" class="gift-link" target="_blank">Darn Tough's Site</a></p>
                    </article>

                    
                </div>
            </section>

           
        
        </main>


        <div id="footer-placeholder"></div>

        <script>
            // Load navigation
            fetch('common/nav.html')
                .then(response => response.text())
                .then(data => document.getElementById('nav-placeholder').innerHTML = data);
            
            // Load footer
            fetch('common/footer.html')
                .then(response => response.text())
                .then(data => document.getElementById('footer-placeholder').innerHTML = data);
        </script>
    </body>
</html>